source.name: USDA Database for the Proanthocyanidin Content of Selected Foods
source.description: The database contains values for 205 food items for the following proanthocyanidins (Monomers, dimers, trimers, 4-6 mers (tetramers, pentamers and hexamers), 7-10 mers (heptamers, octamers, nonamers and decamers), polymers (DP>10))
